/*────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
	NodeBox(AccessibilityNodeInfo node, int overlayType, AccessibilityNodeInfo node)
	Custom class to manage the node box overlay for given node.

	Parameters:
		node: AccessibilityNodeInfo
