	Methods:
		- showInfo() shows InfoToast for given node.
		- removeInfo() removes InfoToast for given node.
		- setColor(int strokeWidth, int strokeColor, int fillColor) sets color for box.
		- showDialog() shows InfoDialog for given node.
		- removeDialog() removes InfoDialog for given node.
		- hide() hides the box
		- unhide() unhides the box
		- show() displays the box
		- reset() resets color, remove InfoToast, remove DialogToast.
		- updateParams() updates the box parameters
